    "content": "A 3-input majority logic gate has inputs $X, Y$ and $Z$. The output $F$ of the gate is logic ' 1 ' if two or more of the inputs are logic ' 1 '. The output $F$ is logic ' 0 ' if two or more of the inputs are logic '0'.\nWhich one of the following options is a Boolean expression of the output $F$ ?\n",
